cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual place recognition and visual place classifiers. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of VPR in robotics applications. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses different types of VPC and integrates them into a Monte Carlo localization algorithm. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with automated map segmentation. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper uses video segmentation techniques for map segmentation.
